verbose_text: To understand the relationship between expression of TSGA10 and cell motility, the most representative EMT markers were selected that included E-cadherin, N-cadherin, and Snail, and the protein levels were detected after the bladder cancer cells were transfected with either pcDNA3.1-TSGA10 (pcDNA3.1 as the control) or siTSGA10 (siRNA as the control).
